name: The King's Dreams: A Planetary Madness
description:
Feeling your way through the Galaxies, the stardust kisses your cheek.
The wisdom of the ages floats through the atmosphere gently winding without corners. 
The angels hum here. A Gregorian hymn plays over and over. Enchanting. Encouraging. Embracing.
The rapids of the meteor showers race, striking,soaring and waving.
This isn't a place you can explain. It's only a space you can enjoy.
Revel in the pleasures of the cosmic plane. From here you came and to here shall you return.
